}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device is distributed by Dutch ISP '''KPN''' under the name '''ExperiaBox 12'''.
It features an integrated VDSL 2 modem (35b), as well as WAN port for fiber customers. :It features 2x FXS ports for analog phones.
